node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

node.title: Watch “The Right One” now on iTunes and ON Demand 🙏🥰💖

Grant yourself the same kindness you give to others. 14:10 13/09/2019 Twitter Web App 7,413 Retweets 20.4K Likes'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 19, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says '@therealstunnaa don't buy oooks until you absolutely need to Outlaw @Flash Scoptumanaa? Sco pa tu manaa? COLLEGE FRESHMAN YEAR'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 19, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'javie @jyoungwhite my mentor asked me "would you be friends with people who spoke to you the way you speak to yourself?" and I was fucked up for 30 minutes'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'W @YourFavvSista hardest pill i had to swallow this year is learning how to pick myself back up & how to cope w/o the ppl who i thought would be in my life for a long time.i had to realize that you have to do shit for yourself b/c the only person that will put you back on your two feet is you'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'dreamweaver @dstebs02 it sounds fake but u really do have a lot of silent lovers on this planet who look at u & wish they had ur ur smile, ur hair, ur humor, ur manners, ur intentions, ur ur poise, or are simply cheering u on. some are just too shy to tell u they admire you. remember that when u feel alone'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Yolo Akili @YoloAkili Sometimes I wake up & have to remind myself: "There is nothing wrong with me. have patterns to unlearn, new behaviors to embody & wounds to heal. But there is nothing wrong with the core of me & who I am. am unlearning generations of harm and remembering love. It takes time."'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Kira J @lamKiraJ weeceo You absolutely HAVE to become ok with not being liked. No matter how loving or kind you are, you will never people please your way into collective acceptance. You could be a whole ray of sunshine and people will hate you cuz they're used to rain. Be ok with shining regardless.'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'VALENCIA Journaling can save your mind, do not sleep on that practice. Twitter Web App 3,585 331 QuoteTweets10.4K Wisdom Amplifier WisdomAm... @SayItValencia Writing your thoughts & feelings down, Give you much more clarity & awareness about yourself. So that you can take right decisions and know yourself best to help yourself in the best possible way.'.

node.text: journaling is always worth a shot

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'If you lost your teenage years to mental illness and/or trauma, just want you to know that you did not "miss out on the best years of your life" and that it isn't actually too late for you to have fun, explore yourself and grow into the person you want to be. There's still plenty of time for all of that. I promise.'.
